<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idb53557dc-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d" identifier="/us/usc/t6/s590"><num value="590">§ 590.</num><heading> Definitions</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">In this subchapter:</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I79" class="indent3 firstIndent-2" id="idb53557dd-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d" identifier="/us/usc/t6/s590/1"><num value="1" class="bold">(1)</num><heading class="bold"> Assistant Secretary</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1">The term “Assistant Secretary” means the Assistant Secretary for the Countering Weapons of Mass Destruction Office.</p>
</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I79" class="indent3 firstIndent-2" id="idb53557de-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d" identifier="/us/usc/t6/s590/2"><num value="2" class="bold">(2)</num><heading class="bold"> Intelligence community</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1">The term “intelligence community” has the meaning given such term in <ref href="/us/usc/t50/s3003/4">section 3003(4) of title 50</ref>.</p>
</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I79" class="indent3 firstIndent-2" id="idb53557df-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d" identifier="/us/usc/t6/s590/3"><num value="3" class="bold">(3)</num><heading class="bold"> Office</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1">The term “Office” means the Countering Weapons of Mass Destruction Office established under <ref href="/us/usc/t6/s591/a">section 591(a) of this title</ref>.</p>
</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I79" class="indent3 firstIndent-2" id="idb53557e0-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d" identifier="/us/usc/t6/s590/4"><num value="4" class="bold">(4)</num><heading class="bold"> Weapon of mass destruction</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1">The term “weapon of mass destruction” has the meaning given the term in <ref href="/us/usc/t50/s1801">section 1801 of title 50</ref>.</p>
</content>
</paragraph>
<sourceCredit id="idb53557e1-47c4-11f1-9665-b3e99855dc0d">(<ref href="/us/pl/107/296/tXIX/s1900">Pub. L. 107–296, title XIX, § 1900</ref>, as added <ref href="/us/pl/115/387/s2/a/2">Pub. L. 115–387, § 2(a)(2)</ref>, <date date="2018-12-21">Dec. 21, 2018</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/132/5162">132 Stat. 5162</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
